PRIVACY POLICY (Watch Radio / Fun Radio)

Your privacy is important for us. It is the company's policy to respect your privacy and no personal data of any type is gathered when using the current app.
There are only two types of data that is shared about your activity, once you start listening to a radio broadcast, a 'click' event is sent to the community maintained radio database 'www.radio-browser.info', and finally when you vote for a radio broadcasts (if available), the event is also sent to the same destiny.
Apart from that, there is local storage of some information (mostly user preferences) needed for the app to work properly that is not shared nor send to any place.
This app links to external sites that are not operated by the company. Please be aware that the company have no control over the content and practices of these sites, and cannot accept responsibility or liability for their respective privacy policies.
Your continued use of this app will be regarded as acceptance of the established practices around privacy and personal information.
If you have any questions about how we handle user data and personal information, feel free to contact the company.